                    <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/adding_cals_table_related_functionality_to_your_custom_oxygen_framework.dita" xtrc="li:18;81:25"> To add an action to the contextual menu go to <systemoutput class="+ topic/ph sw-d/systemoutput " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/adding_cals_table_related_functionality_to_your_custom_oxygen_framework.dita" xtrc="systemoutput:17;81:86">Document
